<div class="para" label-module="para">第120师决定抽调20个团，重点破击<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A4%AA%E5%8E%9F/24334" data-lemmaid="24334">太原</a>以<div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
